title: S2 E8: Rob-a-Bye Baby with Kirsten Nelson
description:
This week we're talking about Season Two Episode Eight: Rob-a-Bye Baby! Plus, we're joined by one of our besties and star of the episode…Kirsten Nelson! This episode is chock full of Psych premonitions, pineapple sightings, and lots of laughs!
